OL,7,FThe jury in the trial of a schoolgirl
OL,8,Faccused of attempting to murder two
OL,9,Fteachers and another pupil at a school
OL,10,Fin Ammanford, Carmarthenshire has
OL,11,Fretired to consider verdicts.
OL,13,FThe 14-year-old girl, who cannot be
OL,14,Fnamed due to her age, admits wounding
OL,15,Fwith intent after stabbing three
OL,16,Fpeople at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman ` also
OL,17,Fknown as Amman Valley School ` in
OL,18,FApril this year.
OL,20,FShe denies three counts of attempted
OL,21,Fmurder.
