OL,7,FOn Tuesday afternoon, Judge Paul
OL,8,FThomas KC sent the jurors to consider
OL,9,Ftheir verdicts in the trial, which
OL,10,Fbegan last week at Swansea Crown Court.
OL,12,FHe told the jury they were under no
OL,13,Ftime pressure to reach a decision.
OL,15,FTwo teachers and a female pupil
OL,16,Frequired hospital treatment after the
OL,17,Fstabbing at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman, which
OL,18,Fsent the school into lockdown.
