OL,7,FSwansea Crown Court heard the
OL,8,Fteenager, who was 13 at the time of
OL,9,Fthe incident, attacked teachers Fiona
OL,10,FElias and Liz Hopkin during the
OL,11,Fmorning break.
OL,13,FThe defendant then moved on to stab
OL,14,Fanother girl before being restrained
OL,15,Fby staff.
OL,17,FAll three victims survived the attack
OL,18,Fbut Ms Hopkin, who was stabbed in the
OL,19,Fneck, had to be flown to Cardiff by
OL,20,Fair ambulance.
