OL,7,FThe girl has insisted she did not mean
OL,8,Fto kill anyone during the incident.
OL,10,FThe court previously heard that she
OL,11,Ftold police officers after she was
OL,12,Farrested: "I'm pretty sure this is
OL,13,Fgoing to be on the news.
OL,15,F"So more eyes will be looking at me...
OL,16,FThat's one way to be a celebrity."
OL,18,FBut she also asked, "Are they dead"
OL,19,Fand added: "How am I going to face my
OL,20,Ffamily after what I've done?"
