OL,7,FThe court heard that the girl
OL,8,Fdescribed the attack on the teenager
OL,9,Fto the officers, saying: "I stabbed
OL,10,Fher, oopsies."
OL,12,FThe girl is also alleged to have
OL,13,Fconfronted assistant head Ms Elias in
OL,14,Fthe school yard, telling her, "I'm
OL,15,Fgoing to kill you, I'm going to
OL,16,Ff****** kill you", before launching
OL,17,Fher attack.
