OL,7,FFellow teacher Ms Hopkin immediately
OL,8,Fintervened and sustained injuries to
OL,9,Fher back, neck, legs and arms, and had
OL,10,Fto be airlifted for treatment.
OL,12,FGiving evidence on Monday, the girl
OL,13,Finsisted she did not mean to kill
OL,14,Fanyone and that she had carried knives
OL,15,Finto school since she was in primary
OL,16,Fschool.
OL,18,FShe told the jury she kept the knives
OL,19,Fbecause she used them to self-harm and
OL,20,Fwas frightened of being bullied.
