OL,7,FThe girl said she felt "terrible"
OL,8,Fabout what had happened and that she
OL,9,Fwould "do anything to go back".
OL,11,FShe said: "It doesn't feel like I did
OL,12,Fit, to be honest. (I feel) terrible,
OL,13,Fguilty."
OL,15,FShe described the events as being a
OL,16,Fblur and could not remember much of
OL,17,Fthe incident, but added: "I remember
OL,18,Fthinking to myself 'What am I doing?
OL,19,FWhat am I doing? Stop'"
