OL,7,FOn the day of the attack, the girl
OL,8,Ftold the jury she had been in a
OL,9,F"grumpy mood" and accepted she told
OL,10,Ffriends she wanted to "slap" Ms Elias
OL,11,Fbut insisted she did not intend to try
OL,12,Fto kill her.
OL,14,FEarlier in the trial, the girl's
OL,15,Ffather told the court she had been
OL,16,Fsubjected to bullying at school, and
OL,17,Falleged someone had attempted to break
OL,18,Finto their house.
