OL,7,FIn September 2023, the girl had been
OL,8,Fexcluded from school for around a week
OL,9,Fafter she was found with a knife in
OL,10,Fher bag.
OL,12,FAs a result, her father began checking
OL,13,Fher bag but she said she kept taking a
OL,14,Fknife hidden in her pocket.
OL,16,FThe trial continues.
